# SkillCraft Technology Responsive Landing Page

A modern and responsive landing page built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.


## Overview

This project is a modern and responsive landing page developed for SkillCraft Technology using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The website is designed to provide an engaging user experience with a clean interface, smooth navigation, and interactive elements.

## Features

* Responsive design for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices
* Fixed navigation bar with scroll effects
* Smooth scrolling navigation
* Modern blue and purple color theme
* Technology domains section
* Features and achievements section
* Student reviews section
* Contact form
* Application form
* Hover animations and interactive UI elements

## Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript

## Project Structure

* index.html
* style.css
* script.js

## Learning Outcomes

Through this project, I gained experience in:

* Creating responsive web layouts
* Designing modern user interfaces
* Implementing interactive navigation menus
* Organizing code into separate HTML, CSS, and JavaScript files
* Building professional landing pages

